## 8. Prohibited Practices

❌ **Direct Database Access**: Must use core engine data management
❌ **Bypassing Risk Management**: All trades must be authorized
❌ **Mixed Architectural Layers**: Keep layer separation clean
❌ **Hardcoded Configuration**: Use configuration files and classes
❌ **Incomplete Error Handling**: Always handle exceptions appropriately